info.name: MusicBrainz Dark Grey and Orangish
info.description:
Makes MusicBrainz.org dark grey and orange
  • with light blue inputs (textboxes, etc)
  • and orange highlighted text.
info.additionalInfo:
Tested with Chrome V27+ only. Doesn't seem to work with firefox, yet.
